Load Data File 7

In this step we will be loading the data file for the project.


Step 1. Start your Power BI Desktop application.

Step 2. Download the attached data file  bi clicking the button above and follow the                            steps in the Gif below.



This is a Microsoft documentation about Data Sources about Power BI. It includes direction on how to load from different sources

.https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/power-bi/connect-data/desktop-data-sources#:~:text=Power%20BI%20Desktop%20makes%20the,select%20the%20Transform%20Data%20button.
